{
  "chapter": 25,
  "chapter_summary": "毛文琪从铁平口中得知毛臬已派十余高手追杀缪文，悲愤中掌掴铁平并夺车而去。两个妖异锦衣老人随后逼问铁平，得知她是毛臬之女，押他去见毛臬。杭州西湖群剑云集，银鹤道人在苏堤割臂滴血，向“缪文”诉说二十年杀父灭家之恨。朱白羽邀走银鹤，程枫则带四名蓝衣剑手引缪文至岳王坟附近围杀。缪文显露绝顶武功，徒手夺四剑、折剑飞杀蓝衣剑手，又在程枫认出其复仇身份后杀死程枫，第一次以仇人鲜血告慰亡父，却也感到复仇辛酸。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping",
      "speaker_name": "铁平",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "师父总觉得他像是自己一个强仇的后人，却不能决定，又觉得他总要对自己不利，但也不能确定，是以这些日子，师父心情极不安宁，到后来……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping",
      "speaker_name": "铁平",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "有一天师父忽然对我说：'宁可我负天下人，毋教一人负我。\n'第二天，就是昨天，师父便调集了十数个高手，去取那姓缪的性命，而且还告诉他们，他们可以选择任何方法，任何手段。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_nie",
      "speaker_name": "毛臬",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping",
      "text": "宁可我负天下人，毋教一人负我。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping",
      "speaker_name": "铁平",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "到了此刻……嘿嘿，那姓缪的焉能还有命在？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping",
      "speaker_name": "铁平",
      "listener": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "text": "姑娘！我知道的已全都告诉了你，你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_mian_jin_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "左面锦衣老人",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping",
      "text": "方才那女子是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_mian_jin_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "右面锦衣老人",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping",
      "text": "方才那女子是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping",
      "speaker_name": "铁平",
      "listener": "char_you_mian_jin_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "你管不着！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_mian_jin_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "左面锦衣老人",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping",
      "text": "你不说，打死你。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_mian_jin_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "右面锦衣老人",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping",
      "text": "你告诉我，你有好处。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping",
      "speaker_name": "铁平",
      "listener": "char_zuo_mian_jin_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "滚开！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_mian_jin_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "左面锦衣老人",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping",
      "text": "你打不过我的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_mian_jin_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "右面锦衣老人",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping",
      "text": "你还是说出来吧！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping",
      "speaker_name": "铁平",
      "listener": "char_zuo_mian_jin_yi_lao_ren",
      "text": "那是灵蛇毛臬的爱女。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_mian_jin_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "左面锦衣老人",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping",
      "text": "那么你就是毛臬的徒弟了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_mian_jin_yi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "右面锦衣老人",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping",
      "text": "带我去见毛臬！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "text": "道长，你这是做什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "银鹤道人",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "仇恨！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "text": "仇恨？……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "银鹤道人",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "仇恨！正是为了仇恨！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "银鹤道人",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "缪兄，你看，这些都是仇恨，二十年来，我心中除了仇恨之外，几乎再无他物，这仇恨偏又无法宣泄，我……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "银鹤道人",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "我只有伤残自己的身体，让心里的仇恨随着鲜血流出——些，否则……唉，否则我真不知道如何能活到今日。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "仇恨……仇恨……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "银鹤道人",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "杀父仇恨，不共戴天的仇恨，仔细想来，却也不是人人都能尝受的事……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "银鹤道人",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "缪兄，你可知道仇恨的滋味！\n它除了可以为人带来痛苦，还可激励人们的雄心壮志。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "银鹤道人",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "你自然不会知道的，不会知道的……杀父之仇，灭家之仇……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "text": "你的仇人是谁？\n可以告诉找么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "银鹤道人",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "为……什……么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "text": "小弟虽不才，或者还能助兄一臂之力！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "银鹤道人",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "我那仇家……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "不明喊声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在这里！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_mian_shu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "左面数人",
      "listener": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "text": "在这里！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_bai_yu",
      "speaker_name": "朱白羽",
      "listener": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "text": "十余年来，未见华山银衫剑客，却想不到在这里见着一位，不敢请教，道兄只怕就是方下华山的银鹤道长吧？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_mian_wu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "右面五人",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_cheng_feng",
      "text": "程兄也在这里。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "程枫",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "我算定缪文不肯放过这场热闹，必定也要到杭州城来的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_bai_yu",
      "speaker_name": "朱白羽",
      "listener": "char_cheng_feng",
      "text": "今日小弟作东，想请这位银鹤道长去痛饮一番。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "程枫",
      "listener": "char_zhu_bai_yu",
      "text": "好极好极，两人俱是当代剑客，难得一聚。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_bai_yu",
      "speaker_name": "朱白羽",
      "listener": "char_cheng_feng",
      "text": "这位公子既与银鹤道长同在一起，小弟怎能不请，小弟本来有心让这位公子与各位多谈两句。\n但无奈酒瘾发了，抱歉抱歉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "银鹤道人",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "缪兄，朱大侠如此盛意，何妨同去共饮几杯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "程枫",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "但小弟与缪兄多日未见，也想去痛饮一番……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_cheng_feng",
      "text": "如此说来，我与银鹤道长只好分道扬镳了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_bai_yu",
      "speaker_name": "朱白羽",
      "listener": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "text": "好好，分道扬镳也好。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_bai_yu",
      "speaker_name": "朱白羽",
      "listener": "char_yin_he_dao_ren",
      "text": "此人来历不明，言语闪烁，必有一些不可告人的隐私，你我坦诚相交，放怀饮酒，少了此人也好。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_cheng_feng",
      "text": "程兄。你看我等信步所至，居然走到这里来了，这里岳王坟上，最多有些祭酒，却哪有酒家可供你我买醉？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "程枫",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "有的有的……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_cheng_feng",
      "text": "程兄，这是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "程枫",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "就是这么回事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "程枫",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "好个不会武功的文弱书生，看来还是毛大哥胜人一筹。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "程枫",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "程枫",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "你……你是……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_cheng_feng",
      "text": "不错，我是！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "程枫",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "仇……血债……血还……",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_cheng_feng",
      "text": "正是，血债血还！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_qiu_du",
      "text": "爹爹，这是第一个……",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    }
  ],
